Usercentrics Unity SDK
​
​The purpose of the Usercentrics Unity SDK is to provide a lightweight and flexible library for the integration of a Consent Management Platform (CMP) into native mobile applications, to enable the collection, storage and management of your user's consent, in order to ensure legal compliance for different legal frameworks.
​
​- Getting Started 
​Follow our Documentation (https://docs.usercentrics.com/cmp_in_app_sdk/latest/) to get started with your CMP integration.
​
- Getting an account
​You will need an account to configure and initialize the SDK. See Pricing Packages (https://usercentrics.com/pricing/unity).
